640
00:48:59,522 --> 00:49:00,523
Hé !

641
00:49:01,691 --> 00:49:02,942
Approche.

642
00:49:04,694 --> 00:49:06,946
Bon sang ! Tu m'as abandonnée.

643
00:49:07,113 --> 00:49:08,907
